data.description: Just 3 yrs young this gorgeous craftsman style ranch home is sure to please. This home is centrally located in Pacific with easy access to shopping, interstate & schools. Backing to Meramec middle school practice fields this 3 bedroom, 2.5 bath has tons to offer. Arriving to the home the front elevation, stamped concrete walk and front porch sets this home apart. The home offers 1800 sqft of living w/open & split floor plan. The great room, dining room & kitchen has a soaring vaulted ceiling, gas fireplace w/hearth & stone floor to ceiling w/main floor laundry. At the north end of the home is the generous master bedroom w/tray ceiling, walk-in closet & en-suite bathroom. Off of the dining & through the patio doors is the maintenance free deck that overlooks a small wooded area. The opposite end of the home sits 2 additional bedrooms w/shared full bathroom. Walkout basement features a full bath rough in, 9'ceiling, walk out with patio door and stamped concrete patio. Pro photos 9/29
